      "content": "i dont think i can just \"let it wash over me.\" it's not like a wave, it's like i'm drowning. every morning i wake up and the emptiness is just... there. i look at my life and i just see a huge mistake. i feel like everyone would actually be better off if i just wasn't here to cause them more trouble.",
